NK039(ti)018:1: // bdud mo srog gi gzer chung ma'i bsnyen bsgrub las gsum gsal ba bzhugs so //
NK039(ti)018:3: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs //
NK039(ti)018:5: bdud mo srog gi gzer chung gi //
NK039(ti)018:6: bsnyen bsgrub las gsum gsal bar bri //
NK039(ti)018:7: de la dang po lha mo bsgrub pa'i thabs 'di la /
NK039(ti)018:8: don rnam pa gsum gyis ston te /
NK039(ti)018:9: sngon du 'gro ba'i rim pa dang /
NK039(ti)018:11: rjes kyi bya ba'i rim pa'o //
NK039(ti)018:12: de la sngon du bya ba'i rim pa la /
NK039(ti)018:16: byang shar du blta ba'i brag phug gam /
NK039(ti)018:17: lha 'dre drag po gnas pa'i sar /
NK039(ti)018:18: bsgrub pa bya ste rnal 'byor pa dbang thob cing /
NK039(ti)018:20: gnyen po lha'i bsnyen pa thon pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK039(ti)018:21: dkyil 'khor mda' gang gru bzhi'i steng du /
NK039(ti)018:22: phud shul la sogs pa'i sa la /
NK039(ti)018:23: gru gsum nag po bang rim gsum pa /
NK039(ti)018:26: dug dang khrag gi nag po byug la /
NK039(ti)018:27: zur gsum du sa mchog phur gsum /
NK039(ti)018:30: de rnams kyi kha la sha dum re /
NK039(ti)018:32: de'i phyi rim zlum skor gsum byas la nang ma thod phreng /
NK039(ti)018:34: rgyab ma la rlung ri bri /
NK039(ti)018:35: de nas rdzas kyi rim pa la /
NK039(ti)018:39: 'bru sna tshogs la byas pa'i phye ma /
NK039(ti)018:41: bdud rtsi'i sbrus pa'i bshos bu nag po zur gsum gru gang ba gcig /
NK039(ti)018:42: snod gang yang rung ba'i nang du bzhag /
NK039(ti)018:43: de'i mthar mi dbang sha dang /
NK039(ti)018:47: mda' bya rgod ma gcig la /
NK039(ti)018:48: skyes pa dar ma grir shi ba'i tsi ta'i /
NK039(ti)018:51: gri khrag dang mtshal gyis bris la gzhug /
NK039(ti)018:52: dar nag gi dril la mad'i mgul du btags go //
NK039(ti)018:53: gzhan yang tsa ga li dang /
NK039(ti)018:54: nee'u le rkyal gyi nang du mi dbang gi dbang po lnga dang /
NK039(ti)018:55: bye ru la sogs pa'i rin po che sna tshogs dang /
NK039(ti)018:65: yu bar b+h+yo bris pa gcig dang /
NK039(ti)018:66: de rnams mad'i mgul du btags la /
NK039(ti)018:68: de'i steng du dar nag gi gdug phub /
NK039(ti)018:69: gzhan yang mda' bya rgod ma'i mgul du bud med chur shi ba'i srin lag dang /
NK039(ti)018:70: ba dan rtse gsum rnams btags la /
NK039(ti)018:72: de rnams brten pa'i rdzas so //
NK039(ti)018:73: de nas bsad pa'i rdzas ni /
NK039(ti)018:74: dgra gcig yin kyang ling ga lnga /
NK039(ti)018:75: brgya yin kyang ling ga lnga /
NK039(ti)018:78: lkug pa'i nang du bcug la /
NK039(ti)018:80: gcig brten gtor zhabs su gzhug /
NK039(ti)018:81: de gnyis tshon skud kyi dkris la /
NK039(ti)018:82: mdun du mchog phur la bstod de /
NK039(ti)018:83: gcig bag zan gyi sbrus pa'i snying dkar bcug la /
NK039(ti)018:85: ling rkyang gsum dkyil 'khor gyi zur gsum du bzhag go //
NK039(ti)018:86: de nas thun gyi rim pa ni /
NK039(ti)018:87: phur pa dang mi bsad pa'i mtshon dang /
NK039(ti)018:94: de rnams thod tshal du blug la /
NK039(ti)018:96: de rnams ni bsad pa'i rdzas so //
NK039(ti)018:97: de nas sngon du lte phur mnan te /
NK039(ti)018:98: de sngon dang po lha mo dang /
NK039(ti)018:99: chu srin gyi rgyal po ku be ra gnyis kyi sbyor ba byas pas /
NK039(ti)018:100: bu mo lter phur ma byung ste /
NK039(ti)018:101: de ma mnan na bar chad brtsams pas /
NK039(ti)018:103: shog gu la bud med kyi gzugs la /
NK039(ti)018:104: lus po mig gi gang ba /
NK039(ti)018:105: rkang pa bya'i rkang pa gcig bris la /
NK039(ti)018:106: snying kar tshe dang longs spyod /
NK039(ti)018:107: dngos grub kyi bar du gcod par byed pa'i 'dre lte phur nag mo ma ra ya dza dza /
NK039(ti)018:108: bdud mo ma ra la nan bya ba bri /
NK039(ti)018:110: de nas mdun du gru gsum mtho gang ba gcig byas pa'i nang du gzhug /
NK039(ti)018:111: de nas thun skabs su phyag na rdo rjer bsgom la /
NK039(ti)018:112: dam sri mo gong du bris pa 'dra ba gcig bskyed la /
NK039(ti)018:113: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas //
NK039(ti)018:114: sprul pa'i khro bo'i tshogs 'phros pas 'gug la bstim //
NK039(ti)018:115: phur pa gcig phyag na rdo rje bsgom //
NK039(ti)018:117: de nas rta bra nag gi rmig pa la dzahkhuga bris la /
NK039(ti)018:118: badz+ra tsan+da ma h+aa ro sha na h'u phatah tshe
NK039(ti)018:119: dang bsod nams longs spyod dngos grub la bar du
NK039(ti)018:120: gcod pa'i lte phur ma ra ya dza dza /
NK039(ti)018:121: bdud mo ma ra ya nan /
NK039(ti)018:123: de nas rdo leb la rdo rje rgya gram bris la kha bcad /
NK039(ti)018:124: thun mtshams su rdo leb bkog la /
NK039(ti)018:126: bsgrubs pa thon pa'i tshe zhabs du mnan pa bya /
NK039(ti)018:127: de rnams ni sngon du bya ba'i rim pa'o //
NK039(ti)018:129: bsnyen bsgrub las gsum gcig tu bya ba'i rim pa la /
NK039(ti)018:130: thog mar bsgrub pa la 'jug pa'i nub mo /
NK039(ti)018:131: ling ga rnams sgo rgyab tu khyer la /
NK039(ti)018:132: sngags ting 'dzin ci 'os gcig gi 'gug gzhug bya la /
NK039(ti)018:133: gu gul dang yug sa ma'i zhabs ma'i sa'am /
NK039(ti)018:135: khyi lud rta bon rnams bsregs pa'i ling+ga du bdug
NK039(ti)018:136: cing sngags kyi shams du ch+gee mo bsrung ba'i lha
NK039(ti)018:137: dang phyes shig / skyobs pa'i lha dang phyes shig /
NK039(ti)018:140: lha rnams kyi kho nyes pa can du rig nas kho rang gshed byed par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:141: de nas ling ga rnams nang du 'ongs la /
NK039(ti)018:143: de nas mtshams dang bsrungs ba'i 'khor lo dang /
NK039(ti)018:144: yan lag bdun pa rnams bya la /
NK039(ti)018:145: phyag rdor 'am yi dam gang yang rung ba'i bzlas pa rdzogs par bya'o //
NK039(ti)018:146: de nas lha mo bsgom pa'i rim pa ni /
NK039(ti)018:147: bdag cag gi phyi nang gi bar chad zhi zhing
NK039(ti)018:148: bstan pa la sdang ba'i dgra bo rnams bsgral nas
NK039(ti)018:149: / sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dar zhing rgyas pa'i don /
NK039(ti)018:150: lha mo bsnyen cing bsgrub par bya snyam du bsam mo //
NK039(ti)018:151: skad cig gis mi dmigs pa'i ngang las /
NK039(ti)018:152: b+h+r+aum nag po gcig yongs su gyur pa las /
NK039(ti)018:153: thod pa skam rlon gyi gzhal yas khang pa /
NK039(ti)018:161: nyi zla'i skar khung byas pa /
NK039(ti)018:162: steng du zhing gi rgyal mtshan 'dzugs pa /
NK039(ti)018:163: tog la zhing gi gdug 'khor ba yangs shing rgya che ba blos rdzogs tshad gcig bskyed /
NK039(ti)018:164: de'i phyi rol du bskal pa'i rlung nag 'tshubs ma'i
NK039(ti)018:165: gur khang 'khor ba nang na me ri 'tshub ma
NK039(ti)018:166: gcig bskyed / de nas ngag tu /
NK039(ti)018:167: g+har b+ha ta ba h'uh zhes pa'i de'i dbus su rims te bskyed /
NK039(ti)018:168: gzhal yas khang de'i dbus su sprul ba'i bong bu dmar ga ba /
NK039(ti)018:169: rlung nag gi gshog pa can /
NK039(ti)018:170: thod skam 'bar ba'i sga bstad pa /
NK039(ti)018:171: srin po'i ya gal la snga ru byas pa /
NK039(ti)018:172: srin mo'i man gal la phyi ru byas pa /
NK039(ti)018:173: gong smad sbrul las byas pa /
NK039(ti)018:174: rus sbal nag po'i pho gu btags pa /
NK039(ti)018:175: snga shad g.yas na bdud kyi khram bam /
NK039(ti)018:176: snga shad g.yon na mtshon gyi gru gu /
NK039(ti)018:177: phyi shad g.yas na byang dmar bam ro /
NK039(ti)018:178: phyi shad g.yon na nad kyi rkyal ba 'gel ba /
NK039(ti)018:180: thod rlon khrag gi zhal zhal /
NK039(ti)018:181: snyan shal gnyis na mi lag 'phyang ba /
NK039(ti)018:182: mjug ma na mig gcig yod pa /
NK039(ti)018:183: sa bu ta yi zhag pa'i mthur chings byas pa /
NK039(ti)018:184: de'i sga gong du zhing bsnol ba'i stengs su /
NK039(ti)018:185: ram las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor de'i steng du /
NK039(ti)018:186: bdag gi thugs ka nas b+h+yo nag po gcig 'phros pas /
NK039(ti)018:188: bstan pa la sdang ba'i dgra bgegs bsgral /
NK039(ti)018:190: de yongs su gyur pa las /
NK039(ti)018:191: dpal ldan lha mo sku mdog mthing nag rngam pa zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK039(ti)018:192: spyan gsum dmar la zlum pa /
NK039(ti)018:194: g.yas pas ral gri mkha' la phyar nas bsnams pa /
NK039(ti)018:195: g.yon pa'i b+han+d+ha lcang lo can khrag gi bkang ba bsnams /
NK039(ti)018:196: mchan ne'u le rkyal pa can /
NK039(ti)018:197: kha nas rin po che'i mu tig brul ba'i chun po 'phyang ba /
NK039(ti)018:198: ral pa dmar ser gyen du bardzesa pa'i skra mtshams su /
NK039(ti)018:199: thod pa skam po lnga'i dbu brgyan dang /
NK039(ti)018:200: riin po che'i zer 'phro lnga'i brgyan pa /
NK039(ti)018:201: spyi bo nas zla ba shar ba /
NK039(ti)018:202: lte ba la nyi ma shar ba /
NK039(ti)018:203: spyi gtsug na rma bya'i rgyal mtshan btsugs pa /
NK039(ti)018:204: rna ba g.yas gong na seng ge 'gying ba //
NK039(ti)018:205: g.yon na sbrul nag gi gdeng ka 'phyo ba /
NK039(ti)018:206: snyan gnyis na gser gyi dril bu 'khrol ba /
NK039(ti)018:207: zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi dang /
NK039(ti)018:208: gla chen gyi ko rlon sku smad la mnabs pa /
NK039(ti)018:209: stag lpags kyi sham thabs dang /
NK039(ti)018:210: mi rtsid kyi re ldes sku smad dkris pa /
NK039(ti)018:211: thod rlon lnga bcu'i do shal dang /
NK039(ti)018:213: rin po che'i brgyan gyi sku dang yan lag thams
NK039(ti)018:214: cad la brgyan pa de'i thugs kar ram las nyi
NK039(ti)018:215: ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du b+h+yo nag po gcig
NK039(ti)018:216: la sngags kyis bskor bar bsam /
NK039(ti)018:217: b+h+yo de la b+h+yo nag po 'bu ma phrag 'phros
NK039(ti)018:218: pa'i bdud mo bye ba 'bum gyi tshogs dang bcas
NK039(ti)018:219: pa sku mdog nag mo ral pa sngo dmar thur
NK039(ti)018:220: du bshal ba g.yas pas gri gug g.yon pas thod
NK039(ti)018:221: khrag thog pa mchan na nad kyi rkyal pa sngo
NK039(ti)018:222: dmar 'phyang ba / zhing lpags kyi g.yang gzhi sku la mnab pa /
NK039(ti)018:223: 'jigs 'jigs rngam rngam gyi ma mo'i tshogs kyi gtso ma'i bka' bzhin bsgrub cing bskor bar bsam /
NK039(ti)018:224: de nas ye shes pa spyan drangs ba ni /
NK039(ti)018:225: srin lag gis g.yab dar thogs spyan drangs kyi tshig bcad brjod la /
NK039(ti)018:226: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer dmar po lcags kyu'i rnam pa can 'phros /
NK039(ti)018:227: ri rab kyi byang shar nas /
NK039(ti)018:228: lha mo bzhugs pa'i thugs ka'i b+h+yo la phog pas
NK039(ti)018:229: sngon gyi thugs dam gyi thugs rje'i rgyud dran nas
NK039(ti)018:230: 'khor dang bcas pa byon par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:231: de nas bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK039(ti)018:232: mdun gyi dam tshig pa dang gnyis su med par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:233: rten gtor ni me rlung gis byin gyis brlabs la /
NK039(ti)018:234: 'dod yon sna tshogs 'phros pas ma mor mchod par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:235: ma mo yang de la zhe chags zhing zhen nas bzhugs par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:236: bdag la dngos grub sna tshogs ster bar bsam /
NK039(ti)018:237: phyi mchod la sogs pa'i mchod pas /
NK039(ti)018:238: rgyun gyi gtor ma 'bul ba ni /
NK039(ti)018:239: me lung gi sbyor ba gang yang rung bas byin gyis brlabs la /
NK039(ti)018:240: sngags kyi sham bu la b+ha ling+ta kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)018:241: dgra bo'i tsit+ta la kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)018:242: rak+ta la ba su ta la ko ro tsa na la kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)018:244: thod rlon gyis phyag rgya la sngags gsum mam bdun
NK039(ti)018:245: nam nyi shu rtsa gcig gang rung gi phul la
NK039(ti)018:246: ma mo 'khor dang bcas pa mnyes par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:249: +amo ma h+aa ka li re ma ti /
NK039(ti)018:250: ma ma ru lu rak+sha re ma ti /
NK039(ti)018:251: ru lu ru lu b+h+yo dza dza /
NK039(ti)018:253: a shug me sh+ri tri du tra pra kha shag rag mo h'u rak+sha tsit+ta sa ma ya /
NK039(ti)018:255: ru ru pe ru ro h'u /
NK039(ti)018:256: tish+tha tista ba to si rag mo snying kha la /
NK039(ti)018:257: rag mo thun b+h+yo dza dza /
NK039(ti)018:258: ru lu re ma ti sa ma ya /
NK039(ti)018:259: bra ma ha sti bra ma rag mo ru lu b+h+yo dza dzah kha rag te khem dza /
NK039(ti)018:262: h'u rag mo ni sha ku ru thun rbad /
NK039(ti)018:264: te khem kha le b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)018:265: sa ma ya ch+gee mo ma ra ya h'u phata /
NK039(ti)018:266: rang yi dam sngags kyi rgyab lha mo'i sngags kyi btab pa'i g.yon bskor gcig byas pas /
NK039(ti)018:267: lha mo'i zhal du tshur byung bas bdag gis zhal du zhug /
NK039(ti)018:268: thugs ka'i sngags la g.yas bskor gcig byas pas /
NK039(ti)018:269: rtsa dbu ma'i nang du mar song nas /
NK039(ti)018:270: gsang ba'i rdo rjer byung ma mo'i pad+mara zhugs pas
NK039(ti)018:271: mchod pa sna tshogs kyi mchod nas mnyes shing tshim
NK039(ti)018:272: nas mthu dang nus pa dang ldan pa la thugs
NK039(ti)018:273: ka nas tshur byung ba'i dus su dngos grub sna
NK039(ti)018:274: tshogs ster bar bsam zhing bdag gi zhal nas thugs
NK039(ti)018:276: 'gal me'i 'khor lo bzhin du mkha' gsang du bskor ro //
NK039(ti)018:277: 'jog pa'i dus su rang gi h'u gi mtha' mar bsam mo //
NK039(ti)018:278: de nas gtor ma 'bul la bstod pa dang bskul pa ci rig pa bya'o //
NK039(ti)018:283: phyag na rdo rjer la sogs pa'i lha tshogs kyis kyang /
NK039(ti)018:284: sod cig sgrol cig bka' yi lung ma mo la byin par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:285: de'i dus su bdud mo gtso mo la bsdus /
NK039(ti)018:287: bdag yi dam lha yi ngo bo la rnam pa
NK039(ti)018:288: lha mor dmigs la dgra bo 'gug pa'i las la
NK039(ti)018:289: / ma mo sngags kyi gsham bu la /
NK039(ti)018:290: dgra bo am gu sha ya dzah zhes brjod pas /
NK039(ti)018:291: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK039(ti)018:292: bdag gi thugs ka nas sprul pa'i lha mo'i tshogs
NK039(ti)018:293: kyis phyag na lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril
NK039(ti)018:294: bu can gyis tshogs spros pas rang dbang med par
NK039(ti)018:295: bkug nas mdun gyi ling+ga dang gnyis su med par
NK039(ti)018:296: bstim la sngags nyer gcig gam lnga bcu'i bar brjod
NK039(ti)018:297: do // de nas lha dbye'i thabs gong bzhin bya /
NK039(ti)018:298: sngags gsum mam bdun bzlas pa'i mthar /
NK039(ti)018:299: mdun du bsgrub bya de gsal bar dmigs nas rang
NK039(ti)018:300: gi sna bug nas rlung byung ba'i kho'i sna bug
NK039(ti)018:301: g.yon du zhugs / snying gi rnam par shes pa
NK039(ti)018:302: mar me lta bu de nag gam btang bar bsam
NK039(ti)018:303: g.yon du zhugs / / yang g.yon nas byung ba'i
NK039(ti)018:304: kho'i sna bug g.yas su zhugs pas bkrags mdangs longs
NK039(ti)018:305: spyod thams cad rdo rje'i sbu gur drangs nas rang
NK039(ti)018:306: gi rdo rje'i lam du tshur thim pas /
NK039(ti)018:307: rang nyid nyi ma shar ba'am /
NK039(ti)018:308: zla ba nya gang ba ltar bkrags dang gzi mdangs dang ldan par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:309: kho nag rnyid kyi song bar bsam /
NK039(ti)018:310: de nas gzung thag la sngags lnga'am bdun brjod kyi bar du gzung la /
NK039(ti)018:311: kho'i srog rtsa la bzung bar bsam /
NK039(ti)018:312: sngags kyi 'od zer gyi de rbad rbad bcad par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:313: de nas thun brdeg pa ni phur bu lha mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK039(ti)018:314: smad phur bu mgar gyi so mal nas byung ba ltar dmar la me 'bar ba ltar bsam /
NK039(ti)018:315: de nas bsad pa'i ting 'dzin gzhan yang bya /
NK039(ti)018:321: dbang chen gser gyis gzhi la ma thug bar du thal bar bsam zhing drug cu rtsa gcig gam /
NK039(ti)018:322: ci nus kyi bar brdeg go //
NK039(ti)018:323: de nas mi bsad pa'i mtshon lha mo'i ral grir bsam la /
NK039(ti)018:324: snying dkar nag mtshams su spyi bo nas rkang pa'i mthil bar du shag shag btang bar bsam la /
NK039(ti)018:325: snga drug cu rtsa gnyis sam /
NK039(ti)018:327: dug thun na dug dang nad rnams pa sna tshogs kyi btab par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:328: khrag thun ni khrag nad phol mig /
NK039(ti)018:329: glang thabs gag lhog mdze 'brum tshad rim nad rnam pa sna tshogs kyi btab par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:330: rul myag myag myos par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:331: rdo thun ni zangs lcags phye ma la sogs pa bdud mo'i tshogs /
NK039(ti)018:332: sha za gcan gzan gyi tshogs kyi rgod ro brdab pa bzhin du la las sha zos /
NK039(ti)018:335: yung 'bru tsam yang ma lus par bsam zhing /
NK039(ti)018:336: sngags drug cu rtsa gcig gis brdeg go //
NK039(ti)018:337: de nas mdun du lha mo 'khor dang bcas pa la bardzusa skyes su /
NK039(ti)018:339: mdun gyi dgra bo'i sha khrag gsol bar bsam zhing las bya'o //
NK039(ti)018:340: de nas gtor ma mdog ltar 'bul la bskul ba bya /
NK039(ti)018:341: gtor ma dgra bo'i phyogs su bskyal /
NK039(ti)018:344: ma mo 'khor dang bcas pa dgra yul du gshegs nas dgra bo brlag pa'i las byed par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:345: de ltar bsgrub pa'i rtag ni ma mo'i zhal dngos su mthong ba dang /
NK039(ti)018:346: ma dang srin mo chung ma mdza' mo g.yog mo /
NK039(ti)018:347: bud med kyi tshogs su 'dus nas bdag la bkur sti byed pa dang /
NK039(ti)018:349: 'tshub ma 'khor ba la sogs pa rnams 'byung ngo //
NK039(ti)018:351: dmigs bya la sogs pa dngos subasada pa dang /
NK039(ti)018:356: ri dwags bsad pa la sogs pa dang /
NK039(ti)018:357: snying dang mgo ster bar 'byung ngo //
NK039(ti)018:358: de ltar byung na bsgru ba pa 'grub pa yin /
NK039(ti)018:359: thebs dus nam phyed nyi ma rgas kha'i dus su
NK039(ti)018:360: bsad las thams cad snga ma ltar byas la phur
NK039(ti)018:361: pa gsum yang rim pa ltar /
NK039(ti)018:362: sngags ring gi ling+ga ltar brdeg go //
NK039(ti)018:363: rtsang rnams kyang rim pa ltar brdeg go //
NK039(ti)018:364: lha mo bdud mo dang bcas pas /
NK039(ti)018:367: de ltar ma byung na lan gsum bar du legs so //
NK039(ti)018:369: rgya la des kyang ma byung na /
NK039(ti)018:371: de ni dngos gzhi'i cho ga'o //
NK039(ti)018:372: de nas mjug bsdu ba'i rim pa ni /
NK039(ti)018:373: zor sbyin bsregs mnan pa yin te /
NK039(ti)018:374: de la bsad pa zor gyi rim pa ni /
NK039(ti)018:375: bsgrub kha zor du byed na thun khang gi byang
NK039(ti)018:376: shar zur la ltas ngan sre mang gi sgo nga'i
NK039(ti)018:377: sne brdol la / nang du rim gyis shi ba'i khrag dang dug sna tshogs blug la bzhag /
NK039(ti)018:378: shar lho'i zur la grir shi ba'i thod pa'i nang gri khrag dang dug sna tshogs blug la bzhag /
NK039(ti)018:379: nub byang zur la phag thod nang du mtsho ram bu dug sna tshogs blug la bzhag /
NK039(ti)018:380: de rnams kyi kha la ling+ga re bzhag /
NK039(ti)018:381: yung kar la sogs pa'i thun rdzas la sngags /
NK039(ti)018:382: dgra bo m+aa ra ya thun ya /
NK039(ti)018:383: zhes btags pa nam phyed thod zor brdeg go //
NK039(ti)018:385: dgra bo ma ra ya thun /
NK039(ti)018:386: ces tho rangs khrag zor la brdeg go //
NK039(ti)018:387: thun rdzas rnams ni ma mo'i dmag tshogs kyis mtshon cha'i char dang /
NK039(ti)018:388: dug khrag sna tshogs kyi dgra bo rdul du brlag par bsam zhing bsgrub bo //
NK039(ti)018:389: de nas zor la me 'bar ba dang /
NK039(ti)018:391: bud med las byed pa sogs 'byung ngo //
NK039(ti)018:392: de ltar zhag tu bsgrub la /
NK039(ti)018:394: snang srid ma mo ra mda' log /
NK039(ti)018:395: ces pa'i ma mo bdud mo'i tshogs kyi nad sna tshogs dang /
NK039(ti)018:396: dug sna tshogs mtshon cha sna tshogs dgra bo'i yul du khyer nas gtub par bsam zhing /
NK039(ti)018:397: rdul du brlag par bsam la /
NK039(ti)018:405: de ni dpal lha mo'i bsad pa zor gyi rim pa'o //
NK039(ti)018:406: de nas dpal lha mo'i las kyi mtha' bsdud sbyin bsreg bya ba ni /
NK039(ti)018:407: sngar gyi gru gsum yin yang rung /
NK039(ti)018:408: gru gsum bang rim gsum par /
NK039(ti)018:409: dur khrod kyi sol la sogs pas nag por bya la /
NK039(ti)018:410: de'i dbus su nyi ma la b+h+yo'am ral gri bris /
NK039(ti)018:411: kha khyer nang ma la ral gri bri /
NK039(ti)018:416: g.yas su mchod pa'i grangs la /
NK039(ti)018:418: khrag gi ar+g+ham bdun nam nyer gcig 'bul /
NK039(ti)018:419: de nas dmigs bya la dgug pa dang /
NK039(ti)018:420: sngags dang ting 'dzin ci 'grub byas la /
NK039(ti)018:421: gong gi sngags kyis dug tsher shang bzhi sngags su brgya rtsa brgyad kyi bar du phul bas /
NK039(ti)018:422: dgra bgegs gang yin pa'i sha khrag bum dang ril dang /
NK039(ti)018:424: lha mo shin tu 'khros pa'i thugs ka nas ye
NK039(ti)018:425: shes kyi me byung bas zhal nas tshur 'bar ba'i
NK039(ti)018:427: lha mos gsol zhing drangs nas mdun du mar brgyud
NK039(ti)018:428: nas ye shes kyi bdud rtsir gyur nas lte bar
NK039(ti)018:430: gtso 'khor thams cad mnyes par bsam zhing 'bul /
NK039(ti)018:431: brgya rtsa brgyad tshang ba yang gong bzhin khrag gi ar+g+ham bdun zhal mar 'bul /
NK039(ti)018:435: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab bo //
NK039(ti)018:436: de nas gtor ma myur mgyog ltar 'bul /
NK039(ti)018:437: bskul pa dang gtor rdzongs byas la /
NK039(ti)018:440: dam tshig pa bdag la bsdu /
NK039(ti)018:444: de rnams ni sbyin bsreg gi cho ga bya ba'i rim pa'o //
NK039(ti)018:445: de nas las mjug mnan pa bya ba ni /
NK039(ti)018:446: brten gtor ma dang g.yag ru nang gi ling+ga gnyis /
NK039(ti)018:447: g.yag ru rtse rgyal du bcug la /
NK039(ti)018:448: khar sbyin bsreg gi thal 'jim blug la rdo rje rgya gram gyi kha bcad /
NK039(ti)018:449: re ba'i nang du dril la /
NK039(ti)018:454: lha dbye la sogs spyi ltar byas la /
NK039(ti)018:455: las kyi gshin rje'i lto bar tshud par bsam la /
NK039(ti)018:456: 'byung ba brtsegs kyi rim pa ltar rgyas btab par bsam mo //
NK039(ti)018:457: de'i steng du lam las dbang chen gser gyi sa gzhi /
NK039(ti)018:458: b+h+r+aum las ri rab de'i steng du lha mo dang
NK039(ti)018:459: bdud mo 'bum dang bcas pa'i phyag tu ri rab
NK039(ti)018:460: bsnams pas / kho rang mnan nas bskal pa brgyar yang mi thar bar bsam /
NK039(ti)018:461: rgyun gtor gyi nang gi ling+ga zor ram brten gtor
NK039(ti)018:462: bskyel ba'i dus su gtor ma gcig gi nang du
NK039(ti)018:464: myur mgyogs su bdud mo 'khor dang bcas pa la bsngo /
NK039(ti)018:465: ling ga gzhan thams cad sbyin bsreg bya'o //
NK039(ti)018:466: dpal lha mo'i dam tshig las /
NK039(ti)018:467: nal bu nal mo'i mtshangs mi 'bru /
NK039(ti)018:468: ma mo dang rig gcig pa la kha zas mgron du sbyin cing dga' bar bya /
NK039(ti)018:469: yug sa la chags pa'i mi spyad /
NK039(ti)018:470: mgar ba dag dang tshang mi sred /
NK039(ti)018:471: me'i dkyil 'khor mthong na dga' bar byas zhing mi bsad /
NK039(ti)018:472: 'tshub ma dang 'phrad na sked du mi dgab /
NK039(ti)018:475: bong bu mo'i bcibs pa yin pas mi de brdeg cing byams par bya /
NK039(ti)018:476: bud med la smod tshug mi smra /
NK039(ti)018:477: de la sogs pa rnams nan tan bya'o //
NK039(ti)018:478: bdud mo srog gi gzer chung gis bsnyen bsgrub las
NK039(ti)018:479: kyi rim pa rnams legs par gsal bar byas pa
NK039(ti)018:480: yin / sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa bsrung bar shog /
NK039(ti)018:481: de nas gsang ba'i 'grub rtag bshad par bya /
NK039(ti)018:482: sngags dang ting 'dzin nus pa bskyed tsam ni //
NK039(ti)018:483: rdo rje'i dbus kyi rtsa ba'i nam mkha' la //
NK039(ti)018:484: byang chub sems kyi dga' bde bskyed tsam na //
NK039(ti)018:485: mkha' 'gro rang la shar bar yin par shar //
NK039(ti)018:486: de nas phyi'i 'grub rtag bshad par bya //
NK039(ti)018:487: phyi'i 'grub rtags rab 'bring tha ma gsum //
NK039(ti)018:488: rab ni ma mo nyid kyi sku mthong ste //
NK039(ti)018:489: nam mkha'i dkyil du phyag na rdo rje mthong //
NK039(ti)018:490: bud med dkar mo bzhad cing mthong ba na //
NK039(ti)018:491: gsang ba ye shes dngos grub ster ba yin //
NK039(ti)018:492: nag mo ral pa can du byung ba na //
NK039(ti)018:493: 'dod 'tshams mthu rtsal bdag la ster ba'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:494: dmar mo bse'i ral pa can du byung ba na //
NK039(ti)018:495: 'jig rten dbang du bsdud pa'i dngos grub ster ba yin //
NK039(ti)018:496: ser mo thod pa'i ral pa can du byung ba na //
NK039(ti)018:497: tshe dang bsod nams rgyas pa'i 'grub pa yin //
NK039(ti)018:499: rdo rje mkha' la bab nas gtso mo yin //
NK039(ti)018:500: rjes mo dung skyong ma yi 'grub rtag la //
NK039(ti)018:501: rdzas dang lung rnams mun pa shin tu nag /
NK039(ti)018:502: me tog char bab rlung 'brug rlung dmar dang //
NK039(ti)018:503: bud med gzugs dang 'ja' tshon ston pa'o //
NK039(ti)018:504: khol mo re ma ti'i 'grub rtag ni //
NK039(ti)018:505: 'brug dang rlung dmar sgo dang khang thog 'tshag /
NK039(ti)018:507: 'grub rtags tha ma'i rmi lam dag tu ston //
NK039(ti)018:508: byang chub sems dpa'i rmi lam ni gtso bo yin //
NK039(ti)018:509: ma dang sring mo'i rmi lam rje mo yin //
NK039(ti)018:510: chung ma khol mo'i rmi lam g.yog mo yin //
NK039(ti)018:511: bong bu zhon pa rmis na g.yog mo yin //
NK039(ti)018:512: dre'u bya nag rmis na khol mo yin //
NK039(ti)018:513: ma mo 'grub nas dbang bsdus na //
NK039(ti)018:514: bud med dag gi bdag la phyag 'tshal nas //
NK039(ti)018:516: ma mo ma 'grub dbang du ma 'dus na //
NK039(ti)018:517: mi sdug gzugs su ston cing rje mor rdzu //
NK039(ti)018:518: gcan gzan zar lo ma mo phyag bsgrubs so //
NK039(ti)018:519: dam tshig nyams nas ma mo 'khrug gyur nas //
NK039(ti)018:520: ma mo nang 'thab khrag gi na bun 'khrig /
NK039(ti)018:521: ltas de mthong na bka' chad 'ong //
NK039(ti)018:522: gal te lte phur nag mo la sogs pa'i dam
NK039(ti)018:523: sri rnams kyi bsgrub pa la bar du gcod na
NK039(ti)018:524: grangs la 'jigs shing khyim nas 'gro snying 'dod /
NK039(ti)018:526: snying mi dga' la bsnyo zhing 'gro /
NK039(ti)018:528: bud med rgyus dang mo mtshan ston pa rmis /
NK039(ti)018:529: gal te gtor ma dus las yol ba ni /
NK039(ti)018:530: mo mtshan dang ni sngon gyi dbang rtags ston //
NK039(ti)018:531: du ba 'khrigs dang bud med rnal ba mthong //
NK039(ti)018:532: bud med rgyu ba mthong na nyams pa gnod //
NK039(ti)018:533: mig ni 'dzum pa mthong na ting 'dzin gsal //
NK039(ti)018:534: thal mo brdags pas mthong na rdzas rnams ma tshangs zer //
NK039(ti)018:535: lce rtse ston na snying po chad pa yin //
NK039(ti)018:536: so sgra sgrigs na gzhan dang 'thab mo 'ongs //
NK039(ti)018:537: rgod pa mthong na dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:538: 'khros nas bar chad 'ong ba ston pa yin //
NK039(ti)018:539: rgyang glu len pa mthong na 'grub thag ring //
NK039(ti)018:540: chu ris ngo la yod na rim nad 'ong //
NK039(ti)018:541: gar thabs byed cing mthong na ci bsam 'grub //
NK039(ti)018:542: gling bu 'bud cing byung na gtor ma 'dod pa yin //
NK039(ti)018:543: 'phreng ba bsgrang na sbyin bsreg 'dod pa yin //
NK039(ti)018:544: kha la 'o byed sbyor ba byed pa yin //
NK039(ti)018:545: bong bu zhon pa rmis na rje mo yin //
NK039(ti)018:546: dril la zhon pa rmis na khol mo yin //
NK039(ti)018:547: snying sbrel thog pa mthong na rang la chags //
NK039(ti)018:548: g.yab dar thog pa mthong na rang la chags //
NK039(ti)018:549: me tog thog pa mthong na chung ma lus la chags //
NK039(ti)018:550: stang stabs byed pa mthong na slob ma'i lus la chags //
NK039(ti)018:551: bya dang gcan gzan gtor ma len na bzang //
NK039(ti)018:552: kha rog 'dug na snying po phyag rgya nor //
NK039(ti)018:553: 'dzum pa mthong na bdag tshe ring bar rtags yin //
NK039(ti)018:554: kos la mi reg par yod slob ma yin //
NK039(ti)018:555: sha ba zhon na nor rnams 'phel ba'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:556: ma mo 'grub pa'i rtags rnams gang 'byung yang //
NK039(ti)018:557: de nas rtag bzang 'byung ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:558: bdud rtsi bum pa'i phyag bcas pa ni /
NK039(ti)018:559: dngos grub blang ba'i sngags bzlas par byas la //
NK039(ti)018:560: ma dang sring mo khol mo dam la btags //
NK039(ti)018:561: mtshan ma ngan pa dag ni mthong ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:562: mtshan ma bzlog pa'i dri shul phyag rgya bca' //
NK039(ti)018:563: mtshan ma ngan pa sngags kyi bzlog /
NK039(ti)018:564: rdo rje'i gsang sngags bshad par bya //
NK039(ti)018:565: dpal ldan lha mo'i srog gi snying po ni /
NK039(ti)018:566: +amo ru ru b+ae ti shu ma he sing /
NK039(ti)018:567: ru ru ro b+he ti sh+aa ba to si /
NK039(ti)018:568: tsa sha ba la a shug me h'u b+h+yo dza dza /
NK039(ti)018:569: khol mo ri ti'i snying po ni /
NK039(ti)018:570: +amo ru ru be ro ru ti shu ba to si rag mo ste ma rag mo thun b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)018:571: ma ma trag rak+sha kha mun tra ba tra ba
NK039(ti)018:572: trag rak+sha tsit+ta kha rag mo ri ma ti sa
NK039(ti)018:573: ma ya / bra ma ma h+aa sti pra ta na b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)018:574: mu ru lu ru lu b+h+yo dza dza /
NK039(ti)018:575: de nas srog la brten pa'i sngags yin te /
NK039(ti)018:576: sa ya bzlas na ma mo mngon du 'ong ba mthong /
NK039(ti)018:577: bye ba bzlas na phyag rgya ston par byed de /
NK039(ti)018:578: 'bum phrag gis kyang dngos grub mtshan ma ston /
NK039(ti)018:579: kho mo'i snying po bzlas ma thag tu 'ong /
NK039(ti)018:580: sa ma ya du rak+sha sing ha rak+sha b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)018:581: rak+sha du rag sha si ma ma ma ma ru lu ru lu ru lu b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)018:582: de nas 'khor nag mo stong gi snying po /
NK039(ti)018:583: +amo ma h+aa ka li ma h+aa ka li ma
NK039(ti)018:584: ti a gad dza ya a gad dza ya pra
NK039(ti)018:585: be sha ya pra be sha ya /
NK039(ti)018:590: +amo ru ru ro ru tri tsa pa la a shug me b+h+yo dza dza /
NK039(ti)018:592: ma h+aa ka li a be sha ya /
NK039(ti)018:593: a ti ma ti sa ma ya 'bebs te lhan /
NK039(ti)018:594: de nas gtor ma'i sngags so //
NK039(ti)018:595: ma ma d+ae bi ma h+aa ka li re ma
NK039(ti)018:596: ti b+ha ling+ta kha kha kh+aa hi ma h+aa pu
NK039(ti)018:597: tsa ho / a mri ta kha hih de nas gtor ma'i sngags so //
NK039(ti)018:598: sa ma ya ma bra ha ga b+aa la sa ma ya /
NK039(ti)018:599: ma h+aa ga li ga ya sa ma ya /
NK039(ti)018:600: ma h+aa ga li sag sa ma y+aa /
NK039(ti)018:601: ma h+aa ka li tsit+ta sa m+aa ya ma ya mu dra ga sa la h'u /
NK039(ti)018:602: de nas dam tshig brten cing gang du dam bskur ba'i sngags so //
NK039(ti)018:604: ma h+aa ka li sa ma ya /
NK039(ti)018:605: badz+ra kro ta karma rak+sha h'u /
NK039(ti)018:606: de nas las la bskul ba'o //
NK039(ti)018:607: ru ru tsit+ta a shug me sa ti ru tra kha rak+sha raka mo h'u /
NK039(ti)018:608: rag+sha tsit+ta ma h+aa ka li yam ti mu ru kha tsit+ta nan /
NK039(ti)018:609: rag mo de gem dza dza /
NK039(ti)018:610: dza dza ma ma dri ti h'u b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)018:611: de nas dpon g.yog gnad la bskul ba'i sngags so //
NK039(ti)018:612: badz+ra tsan+da'ang gi ni ti mi ma h+aa ka li
NK039(ti)018:613: re ma ti ka ya waka tsit+ta sid+d+hi sa ma
NK039(ti)018:614: ya pha la a be sha ya /
NK039(ti)018:615: de nas dngos grub blang ba'i sngags so //
NK039(ti)018:616: ma h+aa ka li ye h'u /
NK039(ti)018:617: ru ru tsa pa la a shug me h'u /
NK039(ti)018:618: ma h+aa ka li a be sha ya /
NK039(ti)018:619: ga ba la dri ni ma h+aa dz+ny+aa na ga ya sag tsit+ta h'u /
NK039(ti)018:620: de nas dbang bskur ba'i sngags so //
NK039(ti)018:621: tri d+hi tsa mun 'gyur te h'u /
NK039(ti)018:622: de nas nyams len rtags pa'i sngags so //
NK039(ti)018:623: h'u phata ma h+aa ka li /
NK039(ti)018:625: ta ka ha na da ha pa d+ha ru lu kha d+ha ma tsa ma ra ya h'u phata /
NK039(ti)018:626: de ni mtshan ngan pa bzlog pa'i sngags so //
NK039(ti)018:627: h'u h'u h'u h'u h'u h'u h'u h'u /
NK039(ti)018:628: hring hring hring hring hring hring hring hring /
NK039(ti)018:629: ki ta ki ta ki ta ki ta ki ta ki ta ki ta ki ta /
NK039(ti)018:630: b+h+r+aum gmo b+h+r+aum gmo b+h+r+aum gmo b+h+r+aum gmo b+h+r+aum gmo b+h+r+aum gmo b+h+r+aum gmo b+h+r+aum gmo //
NK039(ti)018:631: hu du hu du hu du hu du hu du hu du hu du hu du /
NK039(ti)018:632: pha dang ka pha dang ka pha dang ka pha
NK039(ti)018:633: dang ka pha dang ka pha dang ka pha dang
NK039(ti)018:635: rdo rje'i mkha' 'gro'i me lce 'bar ba'i rgyud las sngags bstan pa'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o //
NK039(ti)018:636: de nas bsgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor byang shar du /
NK039(ti)018:637: dur khrod sa la gru gsum gyis khang bu gru gang yod pa brtsigs /
NK039(ti)018:638: mi khrag gi chags chags btab /
NK039(ti)018:639: de nas zhing sogs g.yab pa la /
NK039(ti)018:640: lha mo nyid kyi sku bri ste /
NK039(ti)018:641: rgyus chen gzung thag la snying kar btag la /
NK039(ti)018:642: gru gsum steng du gan rkyal mnan /
NK039(ti)018:643: gzung thag rtse mo gzung la /
NK039(ti)018:644: h'u mtshan chen por gsal bar bsgom /
NK039(ti)018:645: ma mo gsang ba'i snying po bzlas /
NK039(ti)018:646: rag mo tsit+ta rag ta si ra ti ti sa ma ya h'u dza /
NK039(ti)018:647: de skad gsang sngags bzlas pa'i tshigs //
NK039(ti)018:648: ma mo'i snying khrag rus par bsgom //
NK039(ti)018:649: ma mo bong bur bcas pa rnams //
NK039(ti)018:650: ma dang bzhin du 'gyel bar bsam //
NK039(ti)018:651: de nas snying khar brdog pas mnan /
NK039(ti)018:654: bdag gi zhal nas me byung nas //
NK039(ti)018:655: ma mo thul gyi tshig par bsgom //
NK039(ti)018:656: ma mo'i sa bon b+h+yo nag mo /
NK039(ti)018:657: bdag gi zhabs 'og tu 'dug pa la /
NK039(ti)018:658: ma mo ru lu zhes brjod pas /
NK039(ti)018:659: bdag nyid kyi zhabs 'og nas lha mo 'dug pa'i thod 'bring can /
NK039(ti)018:660: thal mo sbyar nas 'dug par bsgom /
NK039(ti)018:661: rta mgrin phyag rgya'i dbang du bsdus /
NK039(ti)018:662: khyung gshog phyag rgya'i zil gyis mnan /
NK039(ti)018:663: gnad dam dbab pa'i dam tshig bsres /
NK039(ti)018:664: de ltar lan gcig bsad pa ste /
NK039(ti)018:665: gzugs ni rtog pa'i 'og nas phyung /
NK039(ti)018:666: byang shar mtshams na bzhugs su gsol /
NK039(ti)018:667: sme bshags bya zhing gdung glu blangs /
NK039(ti)018:669: mtshangs nas brus zhing gnad la bskul /
NK039(ti)018:670: de nas bsgrub pa bskyar la brtsams /
NK039(ti)018:674: srog snying dam la btags pa dang gnyis /
NK039(ti)018:675: srog gi srog skor ba dang gsum /
NK039(ti)018:677: srog gi yang tig blang ba dang lnga /
NK039(ti)018:679: gzi byin blang ba dang bdun /
NK039(ti)018:680: zil yis mnan pa dang brgyad do //
NK039(ti)018:681: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pa'i phyogs
NK039(ti)018:682: bcu'i bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs dam
NK039(ti)018:684: mthu dang byin rlabs ma mo la thim /
NK039(ti)018:685: h'u du gyur par bsam mo //
NK039(ti)018:687: yang bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas
NK039(ti)018:688: bde bar gshegs pa'i byin rlabs bsdus ma mo'i thugs
NK039(ti)018:689: kar thim / sngags kyi 'khor bar bsam /
NK039(ti)018:690: de nas srog dam la btags pa'o //
NK039(ti)018:691: yang bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas
NK039(ti)018:692: ma mo'i snying po tshur drangs nas bdag gi sa
NK039(ti)018:694: de'i rgyab tu yi dam sngags kyi 'khor bar bsam la bazla'o //
NK039(ti)018:695: de nas srog gi srog 'khor bskor ba'o //
NK039(ti)018:696: yang bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK039(ti)018:698: b+h+yo sngags dang bcas pa tshur drangs pas /
NK039(ti)018:699: bdag gi thugs ka nas gdan nyi zla kha sbyor bar du tshud par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:701: yang bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK039(ti)018:702: ma mo'i mthu stobs gzi byin blang la /
NK039(ti)018:703: bdag la thim pas mthu stobs dang ldan par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:704: ma mo nyams shing rid nas nyams chung bar bsam /
NK039(ti)018:705: bstan pa bsrungs bar khas blang dam bcas par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:707: bdag gi thugs ka nas h'u 'od zer dang bcas
NK039(ti)018:708: pa 'phros pas ma mo'i snying po spyi bor phyag
NK039(ti)018:709: na rdo rje / 'phrag pa g.yas su rta mgrin bsam /
NK039(ti)018:710: 'phrag pa g.yon du e ka tsa ti bsam /
NK039(ti)018:711: de gsum gyi mnan nas gzir bar bsam /
NK039(ti)018:712: sngags bdag gis bstan pa bsrungs bar khas blangs dam bcas par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:714: yang bdag gi thugs ka nas sngags 'od zer dang bcas pa 'phros pas /
NK039(ti)018:715: ma mo'i snying po yi dam sngags kyi bskor bar bsam /
NK039(ti)018:716: rang dbang med par las byed par bsam /
NK039(ti)018:719: yang bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK039(ti)018:720: ma mo'i b+h+yo tshur blang ba'i /
NK039(ti)018:721: ma mos bdag la gzi mdang shor bar bsam /
NK039(ti)018:723: srog gi yang tig blang ba'o //
NK039(ti)018:728: da nga'i lha mo 'di ni ston pa sangs rgyas gser thub kyi bstan pa la /
NK039(ti)018:729: lha mo long gtong du gyur nas /
NK039(ti)018:730: dge ba bcu dag par spyod do //
NK039(ti)018:731: de nas 'od srung gi bstan pa la /
NK039(ti)018:733: de nas mar me mdzad kyi bstan pa la sha ris bur 'gyur ro //
NK039(ti)018:734: dus de tsam sh+aakya thub pa 'di ni dge slong dbang phyug zhes pa yin /
NK039(ti)018:735: lha mo sha za rang mo mchod gnas bya /
NK039(ti)018:737: smon lam gcig tu btab bo //
NK039(ti)018:739: da lha mo 'di las sangs rgyas gnyis kyi ring
NK039(ti)018:740: rnams sh+aakya thub pa'i bstan pa la dus gcig tu
NK039(ti)018:741: smin no // lha mo 'di la sngon ma h+aa
NK039(ti)018:742: de ba'i bu mor skyes pa ni dge ba spyad
NK039(ti)018:743: smin no // pa'i mathu'o // bar du srin po'i chung mar gyur pa ni /
NK039(ti)018:744: rang lceb dang zhe sdang spyod /
NK039(ti)018:747: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gi //
NK039(ti)018:748: tshur gshegs tshur byon dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)018:749: bdud mo dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)018:750: rnal 'byor bdag gi gdongs te bos pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)018:751: nyi ma byang shar pha gi na //
NK039(ti)018:752: yang 'dus shing gi rtsa ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:753: mtsho mu le mthing gi nang shed na //
NK039(ti)018:754: mthing shug sngon po'i gur khyim na //
NK039(ti)018:755: thod pa dgu brtsegs gzhal yas na //
NK039(ti)018:756: bse'i sku mkhar gru bzhi'i nang //
NK039(ti)018:757: rin chen sna bdun pho brang nas //
NK039(ti)018:758: mi ro rta to gcal du bkram //
NK039(ti)018:759: mi khrag rta khrag 'dam rdzab ldang //
NK039(ti)018:760: de na ma cig lha mo bzhugs //
NK039(ti)018:761: lha mo nag mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)018:762: bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam //
NK039(ti)018:764: chibs su bong bu dmar ga bcibs //
NK039(ti)018:765: khal du lcags kyi d+r+wa ba mig dgu 'gel //
NK039(ti)018:766: mchan na nad kyi rkyal pa thogs //
NK039(ti)018:767: g.yas na ral gri sdig pa can //
NK039(ti)018:768: g.yon na gdug pa'i thod khrag thogs //
NK039(ti)018:769: stong gsum kun gyi byo blugs mkhan //
NK039(ti)018:770: bdud mo dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)018:771: dam tshig dbang gi spyan 'dren nas //
NK039(ti)018:772: dam la ma 'da' da tshur byon //
NK039(ti)018:773: ma cig dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)018:774: phyag brnyan bdud mo 'bum dang bcas //
NK039(ti)018:775: rnal 'byor bdag gi gdung ste bos pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)018:776: ma mchi ma thog myur du byon //
NK039(ti)018:777: ma cig lha mo nag mo khyod //
NK039(ti)018:778: sngon tshe phyag na rdo rje la //
NK039(ti)018:779: rang rtag srog gi snying po phul //
NK039(ti)018:780: bos nas 'ong bar khas blang shing //
NK039(ti)018:781: khas blangs dam la ma 'da' bar //
NK039(ti)018:782: rnal 'byor bdag gi khyed bskul nas //
NK039(ti)018:783: dam tshig dbang gi da tshur byon //
NK039(ti)018:784: thugs dam dbang gi gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)018:785: ma cig lha mo'i 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)018:786: na chung mtshan ldan chur shi yi //
NK039(ti)018:787: srin lag g.yab mo'i spyan 'dren na //
NK039(ti)018:788: mi dbang smin pa'i sha khrag dang //
NK039(ti)018:789: dam rdzas 'di la myur du byon //
NK039(ti)018:790: e +amo e a ra li ma h+aa ka li re ma ti dzahmh'u bam ho /
NK039(ti)018:793: ma cig dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)018:794: phyag brnyan bdud mo 'bum phrag rnams //
NK039(ti)018:795: mi ro gshib pa'i gdan mchog dang //
NK039(ti)018:796: srid pa'i bong bu'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK039(ti)018:797: ma h+aa ka li re ma ti /
NK039(ti)018:801: ma cig lha mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)018:802: nag mo chen mo rnal 'byor ma //
NK039(ti)018:803: pho nya bdud mo 'bum tshogs la //
NK039(ti)018:804: rnal 'byor bdag gi dad pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK039(ti)018:805: +amo ma h+aa ka li re ma ti /
NK039(ti)018:806: a ti pu ho pra ti dza ho /
NK039(ti)018:808: rdo rje dri chu bdud rtsi mchog /
NK039(ti)018:809: pany+tsa a mri ta dang sbyar //
NK039(ti)018:810: dam tshig snying khrag chen po 'di //
NK039(ti)018:811: bsres pa'i mchog ste srog gi snying //
NK039(ti)018:812: ma cig bdud mo 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)018:813: ma khyod dang bdag gi dam basre'o //
NK039(ti)018:814: rtag tu dam la ma 'da' zhig /
NK039(ti)018:815: dam la 'da' na bsreg par byed //
NK039(ti)018:816: ma h+aa ku kus sa ma ya ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta la kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)018:819: ma cig bdud mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)018:820: phyag brnyan bdud mo 'bum sder bcas pa la //
NK039(ti)018:821: bu yi mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:822: rgya mtsho 'bab chu chu mig rdzing //
NK039(ti)018:824: ma yi sku la thim gyur cig /
NK039(ti)018:825: thugs mchog dam pa mnyes gyur cig /
NK039(ti)018:826: dngos grub dam pa bdag la stsol //
NK039(ti)018:827: ma h+aa ka li re ma ti ar+g+ham h'u /
NK039(ti)018:829: chu skyes thang skyes me tog dang //
NK039(ti)018:830: dbang po lnga yi me tog 'di //
NK039(ti)018:831: ma yi dbu la thugs mchog dngos grub dam pa ma h+aa push+pe +aahmh'u /
NK039(ti)018:832: ga bur gla rtsi gu gul dang //
NK039(ti)018:833: sha chen spos kyi dud pa 'di //
NK039(ti)018:834: ma yi shang la thugs mchog dngos grub ma h+aa sogs nas d+h+aup+pe +aahmh'u /
NK039(ti)018:835: nyi zla glog dang gsal ba'i sgron //
NK039(ti)018:836: zhun chen mdangs kyi mar me 'di //
NK039(ti)018:837: ma yi spyan thugs mchog dngos grub ma h+aa a lo ke khrag chen dug dang sbyar ba yi //
NK039(ti)018:839: ma yi thugs la thugs mchog dngos grub ma h+aa g+han+d+he a h'u /
NK039(ti)018:840: phye ma lnga yi bshos bu dang /
NK039(ti)018:841: nal sha yon tan kun ldan 'di //
NK039(ti)018:842: ma yi ljags la thugs mchog dam dngos grub ma h+aa nee wi t+ye a h'u /
NK039(ti)018:843: pi wang gling bu mkhar ba'i rnga //
NK039(ti)018:844: man gal cha lang rkang gi dung //
NK039(ti)018:845: ma yi snyan la thugs mchog dngos grub dam pa ma h+aa ka li re ma ti shab+da +aahmh'u /
NK039(ti)018:848: bum dang ril dang phyed tshal dang //
NK039(ti)018:849: nang rol glo snying mkhal mar bcas //
NK039(ti)018:850: sha dang rus pa rkang tshil rnams //
NK039(ti)018:852: bstan pa bsrungs phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK039(ti)018:853: ma h+aa mam sa la kh+aa hi //
NK039(ti)018:854: ma h+aa rak+ta ma h+aa tsit+ta ma h+aa b+aa su
NK039(ti)018:855: ta ma h+aa ko ro tsa na ma h+aa kim
NK039(ti)018:856: ni ri ti la kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)018:859: ma cig bdud mo 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)018:860: thugs dam dbang gi snying khrag dmar la rol //
NK039(ti)018:861: ma cig khrag 'thung dpag tshad brgyad khrir rgyug /
NK039(ti)018:862: dam rdzas rmad du byung bas dmar chen bzhes //
NK039(ti)018:863: ma h+aa rak+ta la kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)018:866: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrungs ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)018:867: ma cig bdud mo'i 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)018:868: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskang ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)018:869: bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK039(ti)018:870: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta la kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)018:873: ma cig bdud mo 'khor bcas la //
NK039(ti)018:874: yang cig mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:875: mi dbang smin pa'i sha khrag dang //
NK039(ti)018:876: 'chi ka'i mtshal thig dmar po dang //
NK039(ti)018:877: shing lo rlung khyer sar ma lhung //
NK039(ti)018:878: 'bras bu smin pa'i shing tog dang //
NK039(ti)018:879: na chung mo'i byung zad khrag /
NK039(ti)018:880: ma nyams byang sems dkar dmar dang //
NK039(ti)018:881: dri rgod snying dang dbang po lnga //
NK039(ti)018:882: bong bu'i snying dang khrims 'chal sha /
NK039(ti)018:883: rnam lnga bdud rtsi'i mchod pa 'di //
NK039(ti)018:885: bstan pa bsrungs phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK039(ti)018:887: ma cig chen mo 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK039(ti)018:888: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK039(ti)018:889: ma yi bu la dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)018:890: 'dod khams 'dul ba'i dngos grub ye shes gsal ba'i
NK039(ti)018:891: 'jig rten dbang du bsdud pa'i tshe dang bsod nams
NK039(ti)018:892: rgyas pa'i ye shes lnga yi dngos grub grub chen
NK039(ti)018:893: brgyad kyi phrin las bzhi'i dngos grub sku gsung thugs
NK039(ti)018:894: kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol /
NK039(ti)018:895: sh+r+ai de ba'i ma h+aa ka la ka ya +aahmh'u /
NK039(ti)018:898: bskal pa me rlung 'tshubs ma'i klong dkyil nas //
NK039(ti)018:899: ma cig lha mo glog 'gyu ma //
NK039(ti)018:900: pho nya bdud mo 'bum phrag rnams //
NK039(ti)018:901: ma cig 'khor bcas bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)018:902: bdag nyid mi mkhas rmong pa'i dbang gyur pas //
NK039(ti)018:903: sku gsung thugs dang rtsa ba yan lag dam tshig la //
NK039(ti)018:904: ting 'dzin mi gsal ra ri khal khol dang //
NK039(ti)018:905: sngags dang phyag rgya gra chags zur nyams dang //
NK039(ti)018:906: nyams pa can gyi grib kyi phog pa dang //
NK039(ti)018:907: phud nyams lhag mar gyur pa thams cad dang //
NK039(ti)018:908: dam rdzas mchod rdzas dus su ma tshogs dang //
NK039(ti)018:909: dpon dang mched lcam thugs dang 'gal ba dang //
NK039(ti)018:910: khyad par ma cig lha mo dam tshig dang //
NK039(ti)018:911: dam tshig nyams chag zhig ral ci mchis pa //
NK039(ti)018:912: ma cig bdud mo 'khor tshogs rnams la bshags //
NK039(ti)018:913: rab tu bshags so dngos grub rtsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)018:916: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK039(ti)018:917: rlung nag dgu klong 'khyil pa'i pho brang nas //
NK039(ti)018:918: ma cig lha mo 'dod khams gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)018:919: nag mo za byed 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK039(ti)018:920: mthing nag mi srun khrag gi ral pa can //
NK039(ti)018:921: ma khyod kyi sku mdog nag mor ston pa ni //
NK039(ti)018:922: don dam dbyings nas bskyod pa med pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:923: ral pa khams nag g.yas nas g.yon du 'khyil ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:924: yum gyi mkha' la sprul pa 'gyed pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:925: ral pa'i gseb nas me stag 'phro ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:926: thugs rje'i sbrul pa phyogs bcur 'gyed pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:927: ral pa spyi bor gtsug tu 'khyil ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:928: thugs rjes dgongs spyod cig tu spyod pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:929: thod skam 'phreng ba'i dbu la brgyan pa ni //
NK039(ti)018:930: thugs rjes sprul sku'i 'gro don mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:931: snyan cha g.yas nas seng ge 'gying ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:932: dman mo thams cad zil gyi gnon pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:933: snyan cha g.yon nas sbrul nag gdengs ka 'phyo ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:934: zhe sdang ma spang dbyings nas dag pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:935: snyan cha gser gyi dril bu 'khrol ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:936: sangs rgyas kun la bsnyen bskur mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:937: spyan rtsa dmar po phyogs bcur gzigs pa ni //
NK039(ti)018:938: rnal 'byor srid gsum bya ra mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:939: shangs na nad kyi rlangs pa 'thul ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:940: sdang ba'i dgra la nad yam 'bebs pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:941: zhal gyi hom khung drag por gdangs pa ni //
NK039(ti)018:942: dam nyams gang yin zhal du gsol ba'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:943: rno gdugs mche ba zur gsum gtsigs pa ni //
NK039(ti)018:944: dam nyams dgra bo'i srog rtsa gcod pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:945: zhing chen g.yang gzhi sku la gsol ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:946: chos nyid yang dag don dang ldan glang chen ko rlon gos su gyon pa ni //
NK039(ti)018:947: theg pa don dam yang dag ldan pa'i snam phyed re lde nag pos dkris pa ni //
NK039(ti)018:948: 'jig rten 'di na che btsan ldan lte ba'i khung na nyi ma shar ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:949: srid pa'i rgya mtsho gting nas skem pa'i spyi bo'i gtsug na zla rgyas gsal ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:950: dus gsum ma rig mun pa dbyings nas gsal phyag g.yas gdug pa'i ral gri phyar ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:951: dgra bgegs skye shi rtsad nas gcod pa'i phyag g.yon b+han d+ha dmar po bsnams pa ni //
NK039(ti)018:952: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal khrag ltar gsol ba'i mchan nas nee'u le'u'i rkyal pa thogs pa ni //
NK039(ti)018:953: bsgrub pa po la dngos grub ster ba'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:954: zhabs la dbang gi lcags sgrog bsgrogs pa ni //
NK039(ti)018:955: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:956: phyir phyogs dril gyi pha la bcibs pa ni //
NK039(ti)018:957: log par blta ba'i dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:958: srin po'i yan gal snga ru byas pa ni //
NK039(ti)018:959: srin yul long ka pu ri bsgrod pa'i srin mo'i man gal phyi ru byas pa ni //
NK039(ti)018:960: dman mo thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:961: gong smad sbrul nag chun pos byas pa ni //
NK039(ti)018:962: zhe sdang gdug pa btsan po 'dul ba'i rus sbal nag po phog gu byas pa ni //
NK039(ti)018:963: klu bdud nag po dam la btags pa'i snga shad g.yas nas bdud kyi khram bam bkal ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:964: dam nyams dgra bo khram la btags pa'i phyi shad nad kyi rkyal pa btags pa ni //
NK039(ti)018:965: dam nyams dgra la yams nad 'beb pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:966: don dam bcud kyi rtags su zhag gi zo ris byas //
NK039(ti)018:967: thugs rje chags pa'i rak+ta'i thig les brgyan //
NK039(ti)018:968: 'dul byed rtags su thal ba'i mtshan ma byugs //
NK039(ti)018:969: ma mo 'bum phrag 'khor gyi bskor ba ni //
NK039(ti)018:970: khams gsum khyab pa'i phrin las mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)018:971: b+h+yo ma cig kha nas me 'bar rgya mtsho skems //
NK039(ti)018:972: lag na rdo rje ri rab 'tshogs por 'phen //
NK039(ti)018:973: lha mo khyod la bdag gi btsun par bstod //
NK039(ti)018:975: dpal ldan lha mo mthu chen khyod //
NK039(ti)018:976: chos skyong rgyal mo mi bzad ma //
NK039(ti)018:977: gsang ba'i dbyings phyug rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma //
NK039(ti)018:978: bstan pa bsrungs mdzad khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)018:980: skabs 'dir bstod pa thams cad kyi bstod /
NK039(ti)018:981: bskang ngo bskal pa'i thugs dam bskangs /
